R blog - its simple rails blog system.Its initial version.

Install steps

1.Copy all files under R-blog(any other new directory)

2.Edit config/database.yml - change your DB settings

3.Create DB as per your db settings

4.DB migration - run this command(rake db:migrate)

5.User access information

Admin

email - admin@example.com
password - admin

User

email - tester@example.com
password - tester

6. Start the server

7.Admin can able add/edit/delete categories,posts and users, normal user can able to see post and add comments.


